{
  "info": {
    "name": "Franchise API - Local",
    "description": "Colección para probar la API de Franquicias en **entorno local**.\n\n**URL Base:** http://localhost:8080\n\n**Requisito:** Tener la aplicación corriendo con Docker:\n```bash\ndocker-compose up -d\n```\n\n**Datos iniciales en BD (RDS AWS):**\n- Franquicia 1: 'Franchise Norte'\n- Franquicia 2: 'Franchise Centro'\n- Sucursal 1 (de Franquicia 1): 'Sucursal Medellin'\n- Sucursal 2 (de Franquicia 1): 'Sucursal Bogota'\n- Sucursal 3 (de Franquicia 2): 'Sucursal Cali'\n- Productos con stocks iniciales",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Franquicias",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear Franquicia",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/franchises?name=Nueva Franquicia Local",
              "host": ["http://localhost:8080"],
              "path": ["api", "franchises"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "name",
                  "value": "Nueva Franquicia Local",
                  "description": "Nombre de la franquicia a crear"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Crea una nueva franquicia. Retorna la franquicia creada con su ID."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar Franquicia",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/franchises/1?name=Franchise Norte Actualizada",
              "host": ["http://localhost:8080"],
              "path": ["api", "franchises", "1"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "name",
                  "value": "Franchise Norte Actualizada",
                  "description": "Nuevo nombre de la franquicia"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza el nombre de la franquicia con ID 1."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Sucursales",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Agregar Sucursal a Franquicia",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/franchises/1/branches?name=Nueva Sucursal Local",
              "host": ["http://localhost:8080"],
              "path": ["api", "franchises", "1", "branches"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "name",
                  "value": "Nueva Sucursal Local",
                  "description": "Nombre de la sucursal a crear"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Agrega una sucursal a la franquicia con ID 1."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar Sucursal",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/franchises/branches/1?name=Sucursal Medellin Actualizada",
              "host": ["http://localhost:8080"],
              "path": ["api", "franchises", "branches", "1"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "name",
                  "value": "Sucursal Medellin Actualizada",
                  "description": "Nuevo nombre de la sucursal"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza el nombre de la sucursal con ID 1 (Sucursal Medellin)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Productos",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Agregar Producto a Sucursal",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/franchises/branches/1/products?name=Malteada&stock=25",
              "host": ["http://localhost:8080"],
              "path": ["api", "franchises", "branches", "1", "products"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "name",
                  "value": "Malteada",
                  "description": "Nombre del producto"
                },
                {
                  "key": "stock",
                  "value": "25",
                  "description": "Cantidad inicial en stock"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Agrega un producto a la sucursal con ID 1 (Sucursal Medellin)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar Nombre Producto",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/franchises/products/1?name=Hamburguesa Especial",
              "host": ["http://localhost:8080"],
              "path": ["api", "franchises", "products", "1"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "name",
                  "value": "Hamburguesa Especial",
                  "description": "Nuevo nombre del producto"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza el nombre del producto con ID 1 (Hamburguesa)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar Stock Producto",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/franchises/products/1/stock?stock=75",
              "host": ["http://localhost:8080"],
              "path": ["api", "franchises", "products", "1", "stock"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "stock",
                  "value": "75",
                  "description": "Nuevo stock del producto"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza el stock del producto con ID 1 (Hamburguesa)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar Producto",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/franchises/franchises/1/branches/1/products/1",
              "host": ["http://localhost:8080"],
              "path": ["api", "franchises", "franchises", "1", "branches", "1", "products", "1"]
            },
            "description": "Elimina el producto con ID 1 de la sucursal 1 en la franquicia 1."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Reporte Especial",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Top Productos por Franquicia",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8080/api/franchises/1/top-products",
              "host": ["http://localhost:8080"],
              "path": ["api", "franchises", "1", "top-products"]
            },
            "description": "Obtiene el producto con mayor stock en cada sucursal de la franquicia con ID 1.\n\n**Ejemplo de respuesta exitosa:**\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"branchName\": \"Sucursal Medellin\",\n    \"productName\": \"Hamburguesa\",\n    \"stock\": 50\n  },\n  {\n    \"branchName\": \"Sucursal Bogota\",\n    \"productName\": \"Hot Dog\",\n    \"stock\": 20\n  },\n  {\n    \"branchName\": \"Sucursal Cali\",\n    \"productName\": \"Papas Fritas\",\n    \"stock\": 40\n  }\n]\n```"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}